  "detailed_description": "You woke up in a medieval castle.<br />\r\nWhat happened? Why are you here?<br />\r\nOne thing you know for sure: you must get out of this place ASAP!<br />\r\nOvercome cunning traps, find answers to challenging puzzles and start a war between the two kingdoms. This is the only way you can get the freedom you so desire! We are waiting for you at Questery!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\nYou are in complete control of your character<br />\r\nMove your arms and body to catch things!<br />\r\nInteractive environment<br />\r\nMany puzzles",
